The Emnotweni and Riverside Mall Shavathon and blood drive are calling on all Lowvelders to join them today, February 25, to support CANSA and SANBS in a day filled with fun for a good cause. Find the event at the Boulevard entrance, in front of Woolworths in Riverside Mall. It ends at 15:00. Shave, spray or donate, and stand a chance to win one of two R1 500 Riverside Mall shopping vouchers, proudly sponsored by Emnotweni.  